{"tid":2209390,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一年半前嘅連登又返嚟啦！中共見到不知幾開心！","createTime":"2020-09-19T15:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T15:25:12.000Z","uid":335982,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"26147667e2a99c2db4efe2ea347872899003a584","tid":2209390,"uid":335982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"每個女人都係雞係公廁！<br />\n鍾意派綠帽 鍾意拎塊閪當做八達通！<br />\n班港女為咗錢可以不惜一切！<br />\n但大家係咪唔記得咗年半前班港女<br />\n佢地為咗自由 為咗香港 一樣有出去抗爭<br />\n同大家一樣 用盡所有方法去捍衛香港 <br />\n大家唔記曬啦？嗰陣嘅後勤絲呢？<br />\n和你lunch中環OL? 全部女手足都係假咖？<br />\n其實我只係想提大家 <br />\n唔好又退步返去之前嘅連登<br />\n大家唔好再分化兩性啦 <br />\n請大家諗返起一年前嘅香港人係幾團結<br />\n而唔係互踩對方係雞係雞蟲囉<br />\n大家乖啦 唔好中中共計啊！！！！！！"},{"pid":"3cf0d2c8a72d91e5bfcdbedef50db033655236c5","tid":2209390,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:18:43.000Z","msg":"12港人送中｜聯合國首回應事件 促中方確保賦予正當法律程序權利<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gdhdOS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gdhdOS</a>"},{"pid":"3b96b968ebc0454d3988108dc4b40530d4bd0352","tid":2209390,"uid":330457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"連登仔：連登不嬲都係咁 係你啲新會然搞衰晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5b288db07a43ad5aec263946c035aec981731c","tid":2209390,"uid":179292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:20:49.000Z","msg":"連登不嬲係咁，樓主做人諗野唔好太理想"},{"pid":"d14f1ad302703883a6630eda27f5f5aa5fe99d2f","tid":2209390,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b105016e64b6d08975ec519291f71b27b281e7","tid":2209390,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"如果我地要依賴連登黎抗爭 中共會仲開心"},{"pid":"96194e3aeaa667d94e61197990f8e3acba6b6fb6","tid":2209390,"uid":374180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply